name: VirginiaDemocracyForward
0:
”Alexa, ask Virginia Democracy Forward for the latest news”
”Text that to me”
skdetail:

Developer Terms of Use
des:
Stay up to date on the latest news from Virginia Democracy Forward. With this skill you can...

* Hear the latest Virginia Democracy Forward Facebook posts
* Have any post texted to your phone

A great way to keep informed using just your voice.
